{"word":"χλευάζω","slug":"χλευάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>χλευάζω</b></el> <el>(χλευάζω,) ( φυτ. <el>-άσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:χλεύη'><el>χλεύη</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to joke, jest, scoff, jeer</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>:—so in <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <i>to mock, scoff at</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}